umbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCuv0Gx.jpg&h=db6f75e7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無 website?"},{"pid":"7c8445226cdaca0774cc8c89a401b0c5414c8671","tid":228397,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:20:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔同意，小學生都識既話 programmer就乞得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果小學生可以同個programmer一樣水平話，個programmer一早唔應改做IT。<br />\n<br />\n工具越方便，科技越普及。以前（93-94年）識寫html已經好好搵，因為無人識。跟著有html editor，template同其他工具，一般人都可以整個web site。咁你重要做IT嘅話就要識一般人唔容易獲得嘅技術。</blockquote><br />\n好多老細同HR都唔識IT，亂咁壓價<br />\n識得IT buzzword 果班算好少少，例如fintech，big data<br />\n不過搞錯buzzword入面 ge 意義，又唔可以直接屌佢搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ad4d115ab1a38999f055706401654e67f2fdbe","tid":228397,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:44:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以參考美國 英國 走得好前 <br />\n已經將 coding<br />\n做必修科 , 甚至係小學已經開始<br />\n但佢地既教材好生動 唔係開個死版既 ide <br />\n叫你跟住打 就係教學 係類似 playground 既型式<br />\n用一個超有趣的方式帶你入局<br />\n一步步練你既邏輯技巧 先係正路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCuv0Gx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCuv0Gx.jpg&h=db6f75e7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個細路響美國讀小學，讀幾年都係學🐢圖（Logo）ja。所以唔好諗到咁理想化。重要間學校係Silicon Valley嘅中心地區，好多家長都係做hi tech。"},{"pid":"db62e4969d7657b741946288e6b83ae80424e83d","tid":228397,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:23:17.000Z","msg":"D Software 做得夠user friendly 既話跟本唔洗咁煩學programming <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591213e6bcb5edde9a3bc0ee7653b427d5d0e6b9","tid":228397,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D Software 做得夠user friendly 既話跟本唔洗咁煩學programming <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown